<h1>Nyhedsgruppen dk.edb.internet.webdesign</h1><p>Gruppen er til spørgsmål/diskussion af de problemer der opstår ved fremstillingen af hjemmesider. Hovedvægten i gruppen lægges på debat af designløsninger og opbygning af websitet.</p><hr /><div class='newsbox'><img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon_reply.gif' alt=' | ' />&nbsp;<a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign/default.asp?mode=form&amp;ReplyID=%3C3DmT8%2E2541%24FG5%2E224980%40newsread2%2Eprod%2Eitd%2Eearthlink%2Enet%3E'>Svar på dette indlæg</a>&nbsp;<img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon_new.gif' alt=' | ' />&nbsp;<a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign/default.asp?mode=form'>Skriv et nyt indlæg</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon_list.gif' alt=' | ' />&nbsp;<a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign/default.asp'>dk.edb.internet.webdesign</a></div>

<!-- FreeFind End No Index -->

<ul class='messageheaderlist'><li class='messageheaderlist'><strong class='diff'><span class='messageheader'>Afsender:</span></strong> TJ&nbsp;Fiebich&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href='mailto:tj99@bigfoot.com'><img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon.newsgroups.mail.gif' alt='tj99@bigfoot.com' /></a></li><li class='messageheaderlist'><strong class='diff'><span class='messageheader'>Organisation:</span></strong> EarthLink Inc. -- http://www.EarthLink.net</li><li class='messageheaderlist'><strong class='diff'><span class='messageheader'>Dato:</span></strong> 29. juni 2002 kl. 20:02</li><li class='messageheaderlist'><strong class='diff'><span class='messageheader'>Emne:</span></strong> <strong>I have 2 problems</strong></li></ul>

<p><span class='normal'>I have a form that sends through email. The form has a validation system </span><br /><span class='normal'>that works good. The code is at the end of this post. </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>1) </span><br /><span class='normal'>The user is supposed to fill out all the text fields and hit the 'Go' button </span><br /><span class='normal'>to move onto the next form. The problem is, I dont know where to put the </span><br /><span class='normal'>'redirect' for the following page. Someone sent me a post reply telling me </span><br /><span class='normal'>to use 'button' instead of 'submit'. Unfortunatley I didnt understand their </span><br /><span class='normal'>whole post totally to be able to impliment that change, and got errors. The </span><br /><span class='normal'>correct way for this to work is, the use puts the info in, hit 'Go', for </span><br /><span class='normal'>form validates, of there is something wrong it makes them fix it, otherwise </span><br /><span class='normal'>onto the next form. </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>2) </span><br /><span class='normal'>There is a number field. I want to user to be able to put a numerical value </span><br /><span class='normal'>and during validation, the validator be able to check to see if it is a </span><br /><span class='normal'>numerical value. I think I can figure the ASP part of it (similiar to VB), </span><br /><span class='normal'>but the client side (JS) Im not sure how to do. </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>I think that all. I know I have posted this thing before, so sorry. The </span><br /><span class='normal'>answers I have received havent been very specific. I am kind of a new ASP </span><br /><span class='normal'>writer, so please be more descriptive on your replys. Once I do it once I </span><br /><span class='normal'>wont have to ask for help again. </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>Thanks, </span><br /><span class='normal'>TJ </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>------------ </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;%@ LANGUAGE=&quot;VBSCRIPT&quot; %> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;% </span><br /><span class='normal'>     Option Explicit </span><br /><span class='normal'>    ' declare server-side variables </span><br /><span class='normal'>    Dim strName </span><br /><span class='normal'>    Dim strPhone </span><br /><span class='normal'>    Dim NameStatusMessage </span><br /><span class='normal'>    Dim PhoneStatusMessage </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>    ' check for input received... </span><br /><span class='normal'>    If Request.Form &lt;> &quot;&quot; Or Request.QueryString &lt;> &quot;&quot; Then </span><br /><span class='normal'>        ' this section is entered only if we received </span><br /><span class='normal'>        ' some input from the visitor... we have to process it </span><br /><span class='normal'>        ' let's validate to see if we got correct input </span><br /><span class='normal'>        If Request(&quot;Submit&quot;) = &quot;Go&quot; Then </span><br /><span class='normal'>            ' they clicked the &quot;Go&quot; button </span><br /><span class='normal'>            ' so check to see if they entered a name </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>            strName = Request.Form(&quot;Name&quot;) </span><br /><span class='normal'>            strPhone = Request.Form(&quot;Phone&quot;) </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>            If strName = &quot;&quot; Then </span><br /><span class='normal'>    ' name was blank... give an error message </span><br /><span class='normal'>                NameStatusMessage = &quot;Please enter a name!&quot; </span><br /><span class='normal'>            End If </span><br /><span class='normal'>    If strPhone = &quot;&quot; Then </span><br /><span class='normal'>     ' phone was blank... give an error message </span><br /><span class='normal'>     PhoneStatusMessage = &quot;Please enter a phone number!&quot; </span><br /><span class='normal'>    End If </span><br /><span class='normal'>   End If </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>    End If </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>    ' that was the end of the server-side input-validation routine </span><br /><span class='normal'>%> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;html> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;head> </span><br /><span class='normal'> &lt;title>Untitled&lt;/title> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;/head> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;script language=&quot;JavaScript&quot;> </span><br /><span class='normal'>function validate(){ </span><br /><span class='normal'>    // this is a client-side validation routine </span><br /><span class='normal'>    // check to see if the &quot;Name&quot; field is empty </span><br /><span class='normal'>    if (document.form.Name == &quot;&quot;){ </span><br /><span class='normal'>        // if so, display an error message </span><br /><span class='normal'>        alert (&quot;Error -- name is blank!&quot;); </span><br /><span class='normal'>        // then return false so the form doesn't submit </span><br /><span class='normal'>        return false; </span><br /><span class='normal'>    } </span><br /><span class='normal'>    // no errors... return true so the form can submit </span><br /><span class='normal'>    return true; </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>    if (document.form.Phone == &quot;&quot;){ </span><br /><span class='normal'>        // if so, display an error message </span><br /><span class='normal'>        alert (&quot;Error -- name is blank!&quot;); </span><br /><span class='normal'>        // then return false so the form doesn't submit </span><br /><span class='normal'>        return false; </span><br /><span class='normal'>    } </span><br /><span class='normal'>    // no errors... return true so the form can submit </span><br /><span class='normal'>    return true; </span><br /><span class='normal'>} </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;/script> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;body> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;form method=&quot;post&quot; name=&quot;form&quot;> </span><br /><span class='normal'>Name: &lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; Name=&quot;Name&quot; value=&quot;&lt;%=strName%>&quot;> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;% </span><br /><span class='normal'> If Len(NameStatusMessage) > 0 Then </span><br /><span class='normal'>        Response.Write &quot;&lt;font color='red'>&quot; &amp; NameStatusMessage &amp; &quot;&lt;/font>&quot; </span><br /><span class='normal'>    End If </span><br /><span class='normal'>%> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;br> </span><br /><span class='normal'>Phone: &lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; Name=&quot;Phone&quot; value=&quot;&lt;%=strPhone%>&quot;> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;% </span><br /><span class='normal'> If Len(PhoneStatusMessage) > 0 Then </span><br /><span class='normal'>        Response.Write &quot;&lt;font color='red'>&quot; &amp; PhoneStatusMessage &amp; &quot;&lt;/font>&quot; </span><br /><span class='normal'>    End If </span><br /><span class='normal'>%> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;br> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;input type=&quot;submit&quot; name=&quot;submit&quot; value=&quot;Go&quot; onclick=&quot;return(validate());&quot;> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;/form> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;/body> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;/html> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'></span><br /></p><hr /><ul class='newslist'><li class='newslist'><a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign/default.asp?messageid=%3C3DmT8%2E2541%24FG5%2E224980%40newsread2%2Eprod%2Eitd%2Eearthlink%2Enet%3E' title='I have 2 problems'>I have 2 problems</a>&nbsp;<small class='newslist'>(29-06-02&nbsp;-&nbsp;TJ&nbsp;Fiebich)</small><ul class='relist'><li class='relist'><a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign/default.asp?messageid=%3CMPG%2E178823eb6b24d6198975c%40sunsite%2Edk%3E' title='Re: I have 2 problems'>Re: I have 2 problems</a>&nbsp;<small class='newslist'>(29-06-02&nbsp;-&nbsp;Rune&nbsp;Glerup)</small></li></ul></li></ul><div class='newsbox'><img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon_reply.gif' alt=' | ' />&nbsp;<a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign/default.asp?mode=form&amp;ReplyID=%3C3DmT8%2E2541%24FG5%2E224980%40newsread2%2Eprod%2Eitd%2Eearthlink%2Enet%3E'>Svar på dette indlæg</a>&nbsp;<img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon_new.gif' alt=' | ' />&nbsp;<a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign/default.asp?mode=form'>Skriv et nyt indlæg</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon_list.gif' alt=' | ' />&nbsp;<a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign/default.asp'>dk.edb.internet.webdesign</a></div><br /><div style='text-align:center;'>Adgangen til Usenet sker gennem <a href='http://www.sunsite.dk'>SunSITE.dk</a></div><dl><dt></dt><dd></dd></dl>


